{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Follow</strong> and <strong>Wishlist</strong> our collection of weird fiction and cosmic horror stories:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/STEAM_231_87.png?t=1729167631\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/Nocturnes_231_87_01.png?t=1729167631\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/underline_02_620.png?t=1729167631\" /><strong>!!!  All profits will be donated to help the victims of war in Ukraine  !!!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">^ click for more information</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/underline_02_620.png?t=1729167631\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>I am John Jones who writes this letter my ship is fast sinking with a treasure on board I am where it is marked * on the enclosed chart</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751590/extras/map_05_500.png?t=1729167631\" />Join Captain William Jones and his party of men on a <strong>treasure hunt adventure</strong>! <i>The Little Glass Bottle</i> is the second official DLC for Dagon, based on the first surviving story by the master of weird fiction, written when he was\u2026 <strong>7 years old</strong>! Take some rest from cosmic horror and eldritch underwater beings and experience the other, more humorous, side of young H. P. Lovecraft!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">get a glimpse into <strong>Lovecraft\u2019s mind